6. Workflow Architecture
Critical Rule

Never use:

“Any Form Submitted”

Broad triggers without filtering

GARAGE Workflows

Trigger:

Form Submitted → GARAGE – Service Form

Actions:

Send confirmation SMS

Send confirmation email

Create Opportunity → GARAGE – Services → New Enquiry

Assign staff member

Internal notification

Optional:

24-hour follow-up if no response

SALES Workflows

Trigger:

Form Submitted → SALES – Vehicle Enquiry

Actions:

SMS acknowledging enquiry

Email with vehicle details

Create Opportunity → SALES – Vehicles → New Vehicle Enquiry

Assign salesperson

Internal notification

Follow-Up Sequence:

Day 1 SMS

Day 3 SMS

Day 5 Final Follow-Up

