9. Client Portal Configuration

Snapshots do NOT create the client portal.

The portal is created via user permissions.

Navigate to:

Settings → Team Management → Add User

Create Role: Dealer Operator

Permissions to ENABLE

Dashboard

Conversations

Opportunities

Contacts

Calendar

Basic Reporting

Permissions to DISABLE

Workflows

Settings

Integrations

Phone Numbers

Snapshots

API Access

Billing

Automation Editing

What The Client Sees

Sidebar:

Dashboard

Conversations

Opportunities

Contacts

Calendar

Reporting

They can:

Move leads in pipelines

Reply to messages

Add notes

Book appointments

They cannot:

Modify automation

Break system logic

Access backend configuration

