Sales Lead Flow

Website → Vehicle Enquiry Form → Workflow → Pipeline → Test Drive → Finance → Deposit → Sold

12. Quality Control Checklist

Before going live:

 All assets renamed with prefixes

 No generic workflow triggers

 Pipelines separated correctly

 Forms mapped correctly

 Calendars attached properly

 Tags separated by business type

 Client user has restricted permissions

 Test lead run through both systems

13. Scaling Strategy

When managing multiple dealers:

Create:

AUTO-BUSINESS MASTER SNAPSHOT

Containing:

GARAGE System

SALES System

Clean prefixes

Tested automation

Do not stack snapshots long-term.

Build one master template instead.

